# This collects most important changes between releases
#
	
Changes from release 0.2:

- pyformex: added rotate, pan, zoom and views buttons to toolbar
	    reorganized menus
	
- class Formex: added function select(), affine()
  BoundingBox now returns a list instead of an array

- camera.py: completely reworked
- canvas.py: changed for new camera handing
- vector.py: added midPoint and centerDiff	

- Added lima.py and Turtle.py

- Added examples: Lima 

- Added lots of icons
	
